  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Fade Away With You</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Through endless windows</l>
          <l>See but don’t touch</l>
          <l>I’m chased away towards</l>
          <l>Your open arms </l>
          <l>Between walls of dreamland</l>
          <l>We sit and stare</l>
          <l>And life sings to us</l>
          <l>We clap our hands</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I see my troubles</l>
          <l>Blowing in the void</l>
          <l>As war is upon us</l>
          <l>And our lives go on </l>
          <l>We live in the country</l>
          <l>But can’t avoid</l>
          <l>The sound of bombers</l>
          <l>Above our home</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I can see a figure of the son I’ll know</l>
          <l>And he’ll be strong and colorful</l>
          <l>His eyes will shelter love</l>
          <l>And see through the fog</l>
          <l>You know that he’ll find a righteous path to all</l>
          <l>And end the war </l>
          <l>And I want to fade away with you </l>
          <l>Oh I want to fade away with you</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
